1
00:00:12,960 --> 00:00:14,519
I can keep the evidence to myself

2
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:17,960
But Auntie, you must promise me two things

3
00:00:18,079 --> 00:00:18,640
Alright

4
00:00:18,640 --> 00:00:19,079
First

5
00:00:19,399 --> 00:00:22,399
Cut all business ties with the Wang family

6
00:00:23,359 --> 00:00:23,800
Second

7
00:00:25,320 --> 00:00:26,920
Ruo Jin breaks off the engagement with him

8
00:00:27,359 --> 00:00:27,760
Alright

9
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,199
Fine, I promise you.

10
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:45,759
Ren Ran

11
00:00:46,359 --> 00:00:47,320
Are you sure it's here?

12
00:00:47,320 --> 00:00:49,320
Ugh, brother, stop asking and just dig!

13
00:00:49,320 --> 00:00:51,320
Wait, what did you even bury in there?

14
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:53,000
Something from our childhood

15
00:00:53,640 --> 00:00:55,200
It definitely won't disappoint you

16
00:00:55,479 --> 00:00:56,840
You made up with Ruo Jin

17
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:58,600
This is your first gift to her

18
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:59,960
Of course it has to be something special

19
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:10,599
Daddy, what are you digging for?

20
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,400
Hey, kid

21
00:01:14,519 --> 00:01:16,519
He's not your dad, why call him that?

22
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,200
He is my daddy

23
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,400
And who are you?

24
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,920
I'm his sister

25
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,400
Then you're my auntie

26
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,200
Daddy, what are you two digging for?

27
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:32,760
Hey, Little guy, he's not your dad

28
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,599
Yes, he is

29
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:36,640
No, he's not

30
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,560
Yes, he is

31
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,519
No, he's not

32
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,280
Yes, he is

33
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,480
No, he's not

34
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:43,560
Enough, why are you arguing with a kid?

35
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:44,480
Come here

36
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:48,319
Kid, what are you doing here?

37
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,640
I came to play

38
00:01:50,040 --> 00:01:50,719
Daddy

39
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,719
Are you digging for treasure?

40
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:55,560
The treasure here has already been taken

41
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,879
Let me show you

42
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,239
Taken already

43
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:05,519
Slow down, don't fall

44
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:06,480
Come, come

45
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:09,719
Sit here

46
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:18,199
This is the treasure I dug up over there

47
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,199
What is it?

48
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,400
Didn't you say you haven't slept well?

49
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,479
Inside are pills I specially made for you.

50
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,719
Let's call it

51
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,360
Feifan Pill.

52
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:42,840
What?

53
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,520
Feifan Pill

54
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,120
How are you so good at naming things?

55
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,479
What do you mean by that?

56
00:02:48,479 --> 00:02:49,199
Are you mocking me?

57
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,039
I'm not

58
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:51,560
You're mocking me!

59
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,759
Kid, tell me

60
00:02:55,159 --> 00:02:57,120
Where did you get this?

61
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,080
It's my mommy's

62
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:01,080
And what's your mommy's name?

63
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:03,360
My mommy is Xu Ruo Jin

64
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,439
How about this?

65
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:18,000
What if it's a girl?

66
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,719
Stop teasing

67
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:22,599
If we have a girl someday

68
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,759
Let's name her Yixin, how about it?

69
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,719
Yixin

70
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:30,439
Split the character for "love" and you get

71
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:32,159
Yi

72
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,039
and Xin

73
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:49,800
This is for you

74
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:50,919
Come on, just drink it

75
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:51,439
Tasty

76
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:53,840
Young Master Wang

77
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:56,400
Young Master Wang, have a drink, please

78
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,120
Who's this?

79
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,400
Ruo Jin, you're here

80
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:15,639
I want to break off the engagement

81
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,720
What did you say?

82
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,519
I said I'm breaking off the engagement

83
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,759
I won't marry you

84
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:45,839
Ren Feifan is back, so you're leaving me?

85
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:52,240
Young Boss Wang, such blind confidence.

86
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:55,319
To leave, we'd have to be together first.

87
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:02,040
Ren Feifan

88
00:05:03,759 --> 00:05:04,959
What the hell is he?

89
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,720
Does he even deserve you?

90
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,000
Let go of me! Let go!

91
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,920
You'll always be mine

92
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,439
Wang Wenhao

93
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,800
I definitely can't match your strength

94
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,399
But I'll tell you this

95
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:24,240
The woman you force with brute strength

96
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:27,879
has already had Ren Feifan's child.

97
00:05:33,279 --> 00:05:34,519
The way you look now

98
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,160
is both pathetic and pitiful

99
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:44,040
Xu Ruo Jin, you're such a slut

100
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:58,439
So you strung me along for four years?

101
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:02,920
That's right.

102
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,879
Ever since Feifan got locked up,

103
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,759
I've been in agony.

104
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:13,920
But these past four years,

105
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:17,879
every time I saw you grovel like a dog,

106
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,519
I felt so damn happy.

107
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,879
Whatever Ren Feifan has slept with,

108
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,199
I'll take it all.

109
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,720
What did you make me drink?

110
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,560
What did you make me drink?

111
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:17,360
Something to make us both feel good.

112
00:07:34,439 --> 00:07:34,839
Give me that.

113
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,680
Hello, Ruo Jin?

114
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,199
Ren Feifan.

115
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,120
Ruo Jin?

116
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,079
She's in the shower.

117
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:46,839
Wang Wenhao!

118
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,079
Ren Feifan.

119
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:54,040
She's my fiancée, she's mine.

120
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:56,399
Stop harassing another man's fiancée.

121
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:58,000
Feifan! Feifan!

122
00:07:58,360 --> 00:07:59,319
Feifan, help me!

123
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:00,000
Ah, Ruo Jin.

124
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,639
I've got Ruo Jin completely tamed.

125
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:04,959
Feifan!

126
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,360
Don't believe me? Come see for yourself.

127
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:08,399
Wang Wenhao!

128
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:10,079
Feifan, save me!

129
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:11,240
Save me!

130
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:16,959
Somebody, get in here!

131
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:19,879
Get me some real fighters.

132
00:08:20,319 --> 00:08:21,879
The kind that can beat a man to death.

133
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,079
Now!

134
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:05,720
Ruo Jin

135
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:07,559
Let's go

136
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,360
I'll go get some water.

137
00:10:00,679 --> 00:10:01,360
Calm down.

138
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:18,519
Feifan

139
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,919
Feifan

140
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,240
Calm down

141
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,960
I feel terrible.

142
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,240
I feel so terrible.

143
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:16,759
Is it really that powerful?

144
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:20,080
No need to worry about drug approval.

145
00:11:20,759 --> 00:11:22,080
It only takes one word from me.

146
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:24,399
But this drug contains excess ephedrine.

147
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,000
That's against regulations.

148
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:27,919
Have you started testing?

149
00:11:28,559 --> 00:11:29,919
On rabbits and lab mice,

150
00:11:29,919 --> 00:11:30,960
we've already run the tests.

151
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:32,440
The data checks out.

152
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:36,240
But we lack live human experimentation.

153
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:38,240
This step is absolutely crucial.

154
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:41,159
No human trials?

155
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,279
In such a short time,

156
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:46,240
Where can I find suitable live subjects?

157
00:11:48,799 --> 00:11:49,440
No problem.

158
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,240
We have them.

159
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,679
That's excellent.

160
00:11:54,759 --> 00:11:56,799
But I have one condition.

161
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:57,799
What condition?

162
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:59,799
Before we launch the project,

163
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:02,000
I need to confirm you're truly qualified

164
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,399
to partner with me.

165
00:12:06,720 --> 00:12:09,120
Princess, at this point,

166
00:12:09,120 --> 00:12:11,080
you still doubt our capabilities?

167
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,639
In North City, if the Wangs say second,

168
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,480
no one dares claim first.

169
00:12:20,399 --> 00:12:21,399
Princess, what's this about?

170
00:12:22,639 --> 00:12:23,960
I didn't travel all this way

171
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,600
to work with dishonest partners.

172
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,279
If North City can't deliver,

173
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:28,600
I'll go to South City or East City.

174
00:12:29,159 --> 00:12:30,559
In a country this vast,

175
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:32,080
there are plenty of Wang families.

176
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,919
But there's only one me from Xinai.

177
00:12:36,559 --> 00:12:37,480
Understood, Princess.

178
00:12:37,799 --> 00:12:39,519
I can meet your demand.

179
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,559
Princess, only you can go in.
